<plot>The true story of Jan Scruggs (Eric Roberts), an embittered Vietnam veteran who returns from the war a broken man. However, with the help of his loving wife Becky (Glynnis O'Connor), he begins to find a new life for himself, and a personal goal when he agrees to begin a determined campaign to raise funds for a veteran's memorial.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?609825</url></doc>
